  "body": "### Description\n\nWe could enable/disable Federation based on the presence of annotations from the `io.smallrye.graphql.api.federation` package.\r\nRight now with 2.15, Federation is enabled by default (which is probably also wrong because it adds some unexpected stuff into the schema even if the application doesn't use any Federation features).\r\nThere's even no `quarkus.*` property to turn it off, one has to use `smallrye.graphql.federation.enabled=false` that is directly from SmallRye GraphQL, not from Quarkus.\n\n### Implementation ideas\n\n_No response_",
